title: Waterway Network, Florida, 2008
name: Waterway Network, Florida, 2008
description: The National Waterway Network is a comprehensive network database of the nation's navigable waterways. This data set is an extract of the national dataset representing Florida waterways and water links. The nominal scale of the dataset varies with the source material. The majority of the information is at 1:100,000 with larger scales used in harbor/bay/port areas and smaller scales used in open waters.
